T02TD2239E:114b-1: ma h'a su kha pra ka sa /
T02TD2239E:114b-3: bde ba chen po gsal ba /
T02TD2239E:114b-5: thabs shes ngo bo nyid can gyi //
T02TD2239E:114b-6: rdo rje sems dpa' la btud nas //
T02TD2239E:114b-7: dngos po de nyid mdor bsdus pa //
T02TD2239E:114b-8: bde ba chen po bdag gis bshad //
T02TD2239E:114b-9: bskyed rim bsgom pa gcig yin te //
T02TD2239E:114b-10: gnyis pa rdzogs rim bsgom pa'o //
T02TD2239E:114b-11: de phyir gnyi ga bsgom pa ni //
T02TD2239E:114b-12: de ni bdag gis 'dir brjod bya //
T02TD2239E:114b-13: chos rnams rkyen med pa ru ni //
T02TD2239E:114b-14: skye ba med par nges pa ste //
T02TD2239E:114b-16: h'um skyes mam skyes des ci min //
T02TD2239E:114b-17: stong nyid byang chub las sa bon //
T02TD2239E:114b-18: sa bon las ni gzugs skyes 'gyur //
T02TD2239E:114b-19: gzugs la'ang dgod dang de dgod bya //
T02TD2239E:114b-20: de phyir thams cad rkyen las skyes //
T02TD2239E:114b-21: phyi rol gnyis ni snyoms 'jug pa //
T02TD2239E:114b-22: thub pa yis ni nyer bstan gang //
T02TD2239E:114b-23: de ni nang gi rtogs don du //
T02TD2239E:114b-24: rgyud du gsal bar shes par bya //
T02TD2239E:114b-25: bde ba ngo bo nyid 'dod gang //
T02TD2239E:114b-26: bde ba med na byang chub min //
T02TD2239E:114b-27: yod na'ang chags pa chen po ste //
T02TD2239E:114b-28: 'khor bar skye ba'i rgyu nyid do //
T02TD2239E:114b-30: gzod nas zhi ba'i bde bar rtogs //
T02TD2239E:114b-31: de phyir dngos po med par brjod //
T02TD2239E:114b-32: bde ba yod min med pa'ang min //
T02TD2239E:114b-33: re zhig de ni ma skyes pa //
T02TD2239E:114b-34: chos rnams kyi ni don dam nyid //
T02TD2239E:114b-35: bde ba brdzun par gsal ba ni //
T02TD2239E:114b-36: dag pa'i kun rdzob tu shes pas //
T02TD2239E:114b-37: bden pa nyid ni rnam par dag / kun rdzob stong nyid rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD2239E:114b-38: gnyis po gnyis med bsgrub bya ste //
T02TD2239E:114b-39: don dam rnam par spangs byas so //
T02TD2239E:114b-40: sngags dang dbyibs kyi sbyor bdag nyid //
T02TD2239E:114b-41: blo ldan bde ba der song nas //
T02TD2239E:114b-42: de nas sna tshogs sgyu ma bzhin //
T02TD2239E:115a-2: de nas yang dag mthar 'jug cing //
T02TD2239E:115a-5: sems can don la gcig tu brtson //
T02TD2239E:115a-6: bde sems lha yi rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD2239E:115a-7: sna tshogs 'khor lo thabs yin te ;
T02TD2239E:115a-8: / shes rab stong pa nyid du brjod //
T02TD2239E:115a-9: de ni bdag nyid bsgrub byar 'dod //
T02TD2239E:115a-10: phyi nang dag pa de nyid ni //
T02TD2239E:115a-11: shes rab thabs kyi bdag nyid de //
T02TD2239E:115a-12: bde ba gnas med rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD2239E:115a-13: mdor bsdus 'di ltar shes par bya //
T02TD2239E:115a-15: yod pa ma yin stong nyid min //
T02TD2239E:115a-16: rang bzhin med pa'i rang bzhin can //
T02TD2239E:115a-17: snang ba lha yi rnal 'byor yin //
T02TD2239E:115a-18: ji lta ji ltar snang gyur pa //
T02TD2239E:115a-19: de lta de ni stong nyid bdag / gnyis dang gnyis med shes pa gang //
T02TD2239E:115a-20: de ni de yi bag chags bral //
T02TD2239E:115a-21: rnal 'byor he ru'i nga rgyal byed //
T02TD2239E:115a-22: he ru ka don la rab gnas //
T02TD2239E:115a-23: dngos 'di bla mar byas nas su //
T02TD2239E:115a-24: seng ge lta bur sa steng rgyu //
T02TD2239E:115a-25: gang zhig rgyal ba rnams kyi dag pa sna tshogs 'di dag kun nas rtag tu snang //
T02TD2239E:115a-26: gzod nas ma skyes mi 'jig bskal pa bye bar rang dang gzhan du rtog pa spangs pa yi //
T02TD2239E:115a-27: bden pa brdzun par snang ba srid dang zhi bar mnyam pa nyid du gnyis med rang bzhin phyir //
T02TD2239E:115a-28: 'di ni 'khor lo'i bdag po rgyal ba'i yon tan thub dbang rdo rje mkha' 'gro nges par 'gyur //
T02TD2239E:115a-29: bde ba chen po gsal ba slob dpon aa wa dh'u t'i pa dpal gnyis su med pa'i rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2239E:115a-31: // / bla ma badzra p'a ni dang /
